<td>Designer</td>
<td>Open</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="text-align: center;">2</td>
<td>Create a BCF issue and assign it to the responsible party</td>
<td>Project Manager</td>
<td>Open</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="text-align: center;">3</td>
<td>Responsible party receives notification of issue and reviews it</td>
